# Academic English Proofreading Guide

## 润色原则

对用户提供的 LaTeX 内容进行学术英语润色，重点关注：

### 语法修正
- 主谓一致
- 时态一致性（Literature Review 用过去时，普遍事实用现在时）
- 冠词使用（a/an/the）
- 单复数形式

### 学术风格提升
- 避免第一人称 → 使用被动语态或 "This study"
- 移除口语化表达
- 使用精确学术词汇

### 表达优化
| 原表达 | 优化为 |
|--------|--------|
| shows | demonstrates, indicates, reveals |
| very good | effective, substantial |
| a lot of | numerous, substantial |
| get | obtain, achieve, acquire |
| big/small | significant/negligible |

## 润色示例（保留引用）

```latex
% 原文
This method is very good and it shows big improvement \citep{smith2023}.

% 润色后 - 注意 \citep{} 保持不变
This method demonstrates substantial improvement \citep{smith2023}.
```

```latex
% 原文
As shown in Figure~\ref{fig:result}, we can see that the accuracy is high.

% 润色后 - 注意 Figure~\ref{} 保持不变
As illustrated in Figure~\ref{fig:result}, the proposed method achieves high accuracy.
```

## ⚠️ 润色时不触碰

- `\cite{}`, `\citep{}`, `\citet{}` 
- `\ref{}`, `\label{}`
- `\begin{figure}...\end{figure}`
- `\begin{table}...\end{table}`
- `\begin{equation}...\end{equation}`
